meta.name: Moon: Nature's Secret Force
meta.description: Series examining the effect of the Moon on life on Earth.

videos.title: Guided by the Moon
videos.overview: A look at how, across land, sea and sky, animals follow the Moon's hidden forces to navigate epic journeys across the planet.
